7:12.000Z","msg":"國際社會幾日前先聽你講過歷史文件不俱任何實際意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次真係衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b34e12da938f29705d00139ccc1885b379526d","tid":309280,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咖哩:歷史文件不具有任何現實意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱想講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366d2bd96855d558dc25eedba088f579c3a00476","tid":309280,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"今天的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da32be426e198c811fb3187dd87a90b92a9a28c6","tid":309280,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"口交部不嬲都無人理架啦"},{"pid":"1c4360bbdc2a02471dee33fe6cb78632bcf0e022","tid":309280,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"歷史文件洗撚守咩"},{"pid":"615229434d2d465f41b9dda59d956bf0e724f4d5","tid":309280,"uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"其實呢， 早在蒙古打到歐洲果時呢 成個歐洲已經係中國㗎喇。"},{"pid":"26a44cac4e40f9c180d17d03eb726e01c3295842","tid":309280,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:59:30.000Z","msg":"已經係歷史文件, 不具有現實義意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa5aa80b7ebaf8230ee64b486c15757f27405a8","tid":309280,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日:<br />\n<br />\n《中英聯合聲明》作為一個歷史文件，不具有任何現實意義，對中國中央政府對香港特區的管理也不具備任何約束力。英方對回歸後的香港沒有主權，沒有治權，也沒有監督權。希望上述人士認清現實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1474476.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3